iwork.eheap2
Interface EventRegistration

public interface EventRegistration

A class with this interface is returned by EventHeap.registerForEvents(Event[], EventCallback) as a handle to allow deregistering for the specified events.

Method Summary
 void deregister()
          Calling this stops receipt of the events requested by a call to EventHeap.registerForEvents(Event[],EventCallback) which returned the object with this interface.
